{"tid":2257899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[奇文共賞] 支共邏輯學之612無錢唔好捐","createTime":"2020-10-25T14:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T16:57:38.000Z","uid":81236,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"432dc91e1afe3f8851503a42709319380932d9e0","tid":2257899,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"第一個就遠近馳名各位網友<br />\n咁你捐左比蕭生未？<br />\n法治已死係咪就唔洗理？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FOepmi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FOepmi.png&h=f4271d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二個仲好笑<br />\n黑狗出幾十億OT你唔講？<br />\n佢地先係運動既最大得益者<br />\n真正既收左錢，黑手又唔需要負法律責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XfLsKmj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXfLsKmj.png&h=4a9384ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三個就一黎好似好有道理咁<br />\n付出同收穫唔成正比<br />\n都係既，坐定定係屋企做豬等宰就最舒服<br />\n等其他人付出前線就最實際<br />\n再係網上笑人送頭就最大收穫了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQF8tNZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQF8tNZ.png&h=db9a22ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明知法治已死既點解仲要支持係制度下抗爭？<br />\n請問你有冇交稅？有交稅既其實都係出糧比港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇用水電煤？其實都係間接支持緊制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應對呢班表面就香港人，實際就中國人<br />\n行動就係最實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【 612基金財政狀況 - 吳靄儀 】 <br />\n摘要：//自6月以來，基金的開支急速上升，升幅最大的項目為法律費用資助、法援分擔費資助、和還押在囚物資的補貼。以8月底的數字，這三項支出的總額分別為$53,527,655、$6,994,378、$3,532,307。&hellip;&hellip;基金當前存款約$36,000,000，需要市民一如既往，不離不棄繼續支持，才能應付未來18個月的支出和維持財政穩健。//<br />\n【捐款】 <a href=\"http://612fund.hk/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fdonate&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PViy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=6ba1dc8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">612fund.hk/donate</a><br />\n【612人道支援基金財務及工作簡報】 <a href=\"https://612fund.hk/zh/latest-report\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fzh%2Flatest-report&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PViy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=6f857743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://612fund.hk/zh/latest-report</a><br />\n蘋果日報全文連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/....../LIVKPZYJKZA2LLXZRU2HSKBU7E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F......%2FLIVKPZYJKZA2LLXZRU2HSKBU7E%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PViy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=2139a02f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F......%2FLIVKPZYJKZA2LLXZRU2HSKBU7E%2F&h=2965b8ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/....../LIVKPZYJKZA2LLXZRU2HSKBU7E/</a>"},{"pid":"fca6cffe84c006e8e2da7ff09631e3a2661d2fe7","tid":2257899,"uid":3860,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月真係五毛共舞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4170265ddfea1a6e9cddd923cb0a55c18e74e0","tid":2257899,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cf5be36b74b3c08c8ba369b4524a753128277c","tid":2257899,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"五毛快入黎駁我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4991861839a880d56d3bebb6ca6beae18ad481b6","tid":2257899,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3734197a71fc6836cf1128d1f1208656b7cedea5","tid":2257899,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"已有一隻上連登既豬負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2a346e3a560